  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic Implant Wear Debris CFD Credibility Assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD-based prediction of wear-debris particle transport in a total knee replacement (TKR) joint space under physiological loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict relative particle distribution patterns at Model Risk Level 3 for a Class II orthopedic implant. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at MRL 3. Decision: Accepted.",
