      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) is a commercially validated code with documented SQA procedures including version control, regression test suite, and release validation reports. The simulation workflow scripts are maintained under Git version control with tagged releases. An independent SQA audit confirmed compliance with FDA-recognized software validation guidance (FDA 2002). Achieved level 3 exceeds the MRL 3 requirement of level 2.",
