      "rationale": "Code verification was performed by comparing solver solutions to three analytical benchmark cases: Stokes flow between parallel plates, Poiseuille flow in a circular tube, and Stokes drag on a sphere. Errors were below 0.5% for all benchmarks. Manufacturer verification documentation for ANSYS Fluent supplemented internal verification activities. Achieved level 2 meets the MRL 3 requirement.",
