      "rationale": "A formal GCI study on three systematically refined meshes (refinement ratio 2.0) demonstrated GCI < 3.4% on all quantities of interest. Apparent order of convergence (p = 1.94) is consistent with the second-order spatial discretization scheme employed. Time-step sensitivity was also assessed; halving the time step changed peak velocity by < 0.8%. Achieved level 3 exceeds the MRL 3 requirement of level 2.",
