      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments were conducted in a full-scale TKR joint simulator at 37 °C with bovine synovial fluid substitute calibrated to match target viscosity range. Loading profiles replicated ISO 14243-1 walking-gait waveform and two supplementary conditions. Fluid temperature, viscosity, and particle size distribution were measured and documented for each test run. Achieved level 2 meets the MRL 3 requirement.",
