      "rationale": "The model employs incompressible Navier-Stokes equations with a non-Newtonian viscosity model (Carreau-Yasuda fit to measured synovial fluid rheology) and a Lagrangian discrete-phase model for particle tracking. Model form selection is justified by literature review of synovial fluid mechanics and validated against PIV data. Alternative model forms (Newtonian, Euler-Euler) were evaluated and shown to produce larger errors. Achieved level 3 exceeds the MRL 3 requirement of level 2.",
